{"tid":1981883,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】北韓領導人金正恩心血管手術後　傳病危搶救中","createTime":"2020-04-21T02:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T07:14:27.000Z","uid":66271,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"1afdcdf356ab0ff5da8c564a0cb25a3723385773","tid":1981883,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:23:39.000Z","msg":"美國情報消息指出 ，北韓領導人金正恩在動完心血管手術後， 情況危急。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線電視新聞網（CNN&nbsp;）報導，根據了解此事的美國官員指 ，北韓領導人金正恩在接受心血管手術後，健康出現重大的危機，現在正在搶救中。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩上次在公開場合現身，是在11日主持勞動黨會議，但12日未出席最高人民會議，也缺席了15日的北韓重要紀念日「太陽節」的活動，是金正恩自2012年就任至今首度缺席，引發外界猜測其健康狀況"},{"pid":"1adb744304229e5b73b96d142b3b4dc6ab214ac5","tid":1981883,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f8f11d2a9b443137ea8f668ecdd8f9de07154f","tid":1981883,"uid":288803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"死肥仔"},{"pid":"fbba8213c240354cd6a2fda542135f19c7f8d361","tid":1981883,"uid":355943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b79448afe9a027efee0504397e63371f928edc","tid":1981883,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179c5f260fa79c4e66bed44df9dec55ab2e26188","tid":1981883,"uid":10199,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i-epochtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1000/s/i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2011/12/1112290404141497-450x324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi-epochtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1000%2Fs%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F12%2F1112290404141497-450x324.jpg&h=3b24cff4&s={SI